title: "EYE-LEAN (Locomotion, Exploration, Action and Navigation with Eye Tracking): a Behavioral Research Toolkit for Data Rich Virtual Reality Experiments"
message: "If you use Eye_lean in research, please cite this toolkit and the underlying algorithms (LHIPA: Duchowski 2020; RIPA2: Jayawardena, Jayawardana & Gwizdka 2025; LF/HF Butterworth/FFT/DWT: Duchowski 2026; K-coefficient: Krejtz 2016 PLoS ONE; SGE/GTE: Krejtz 2015 + Shiferaw, Downey & Crewther 2019; I-VT: Salvucci & Goldberg 2000)."
